@startuml uc-6
autonumber
skinparam maxMessageSize 150
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10

actor "ÖİDB Staff" as Staff

box "Presentation Layer" #LightCyan
participant "OidbDashboardUI" as UI
end box

box "Business Logic Layer" #LightYellow
participant "FinalizationController" as Controller
participant "EmailNotificationManager" as EmailService
end box

box "Data Access Layer" #LightGreen
participant "BoardDecision" as DecisionDB
participant "TransferApplication" as AppDB
participant "Notification" as LogDB
end box

box "External Services" #LightGray
participant "Email API Service" as ExternalEmail
end box

== Retrieve & Review Decisions ==

Staff -> UI: Select application cycle (e.g., "2025 Fall Intake")
activate UI

UI -> Controller: fetchFinalDecisions(cycleId)
activate Controller

Controller -> DecisionDB: retrieve decisions for cycle
activate DecisionDB

alt Invalid or Missing Faculty Data (Exception 3-EX)
    DecisionDB --> Controller: Data corrupted/incomplete
    Controller --> UI: Error (Missing Data)
    UI --> Staff: Display error message & halt publication. Prompt to verify.
else Valid Data
    DecisionDB --> Controller: Return list of Faculty Board decisions (Accepted/Waitlisted/Rejected)
    deactivate DecisionDB
    
    Controller --> UI: Return decision data
    UI --> Staff: Display decision data for review
end

deactivate Controller
deactivate UI

== Publish & Notify ==

Staff -> UI: Click "Sonucu Paylaş" (Publish Results)
activate UI

UI -> Controller: publishResults(cycleId)
activate Controller

Controller -> AppDB: update finalDecision status for all applicants
activate AppDB
AppDB --> Controller: Status update successful
deactivate AppDB

Controller -> Controller: triggerNotifications()
Controller -> EmailService: sendStatusUpdate(recipientEmail, message)
activate EmailService

EmailService -> ExternalEmail: Send bulk emails via SMTP
activate ExternalEmail

alt Notification Failure (Exception 7-EX)
    ExternalEmail --> EmailService: Delivery Failure (Network/Invalid Email)
    EmailService -> LogDB: Log failed attempts (status = "Failed")
    activate LogDB
    LogDB --> EmailService: Log saved
    deactivate LogDB
    
    EmailService --> Controller: Return failure summary
    Controller --> UI: Publish Complete with Notification Errors
    UI --> Staff: Display summary report of failed notifications
else Notification Success
    ExternalEmail --> EmailService: Success
    deactivate ExternalEmail
    EmailService -> LogDB: Log successful delivery (status = "Sent")
    activate LogDB
    LogDB --> EmailService: Log saved
    deactivate LogDB
    
    EmailService --> Controller: Notifications sent successfully
    deactivate EmailService
    
    Controller --> UI: Finalization Complete
    UI --> Staff: Display confirmation: "Finalization successfully completed. Results have been published."
end

deactivate Controller
deactivate UI

@enduml